{"tid":2012062,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果蘋果日報唔保護談論香港獨立既人既言論自由，我會退訂","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T14:12:46.000Z","uid":35910,"like":42,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5c86f04795ebc142139e01057d8a080d67940b","tid":2012062,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"Myradio肥佬黎將香港獨立視為中共、港共同黑警既陰謀，絕對係老舊既論調。<br />\n<br />\n每人都應該有談論獨立既言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span></strong></span>唔係咁既意思！<br />\n<br />\n獨派，本土派都係黃圈自己人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山</span></strong></span>呢？又去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n要求肥佬黎收返該言論，尊重他人言論自由並道歉。<br />\n<br />\n我一個勢弱言輕，希望大家團結，蘋果必須尊重獨派立場！"},{"pid":"5b15d0a42de45ba3d8521d13bbfe6ca58c4e5b20","tid":2012062,"uid":247719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe1bb90e099c3e3bf2021d63a04616c950c96a29","tid":2012062,"uid":82267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"關myradio咩事"},{"pid":"4f3cb96647d5c59285dcbe3ba44a692d66deee5b","tid":2012062,"uid":35910,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"fe1bb90e099c3e3bf2021d63a04616c950c96a29","tid":2012062,"uid":82267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"關myradio咩事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"打得唔好<br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎上劉細良Myradio個節目公開批評港獨係中共陰謀。<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌返左20142016咁，嚇撚死。"},{"pid":"afaafe461e85906951ec4b290503eac94548ba10","tid":2012062,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f616aa3196261e901fc2c62d501648b7afc8719","tid":2012062,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"訂閱 蘋果動 既人畀錢果一刻<br />\n已經否定左 本土派 / 本土主義<img src=\"/ass